songs.title: Salute
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1. Bohemia]

Jive kali rattan ch pandi oos
Cluban ch nachan na bai galiyan ch mere dost
Daru nal rajjan na nale kudiyan nu vakh chare josh
Rockstar munde mere dost five star ch ran karan shows
Kadi kaddan benz kadi kaddan Porsche
Gadiyan ch rivaaj purana zor nal vaje mera gana
Meri beat heroin mere lyrics marijuana
Mera mukabla mainstream nal kive karsakdae tu
Pata kini kudiyan te main vahn permanently tattooed
Hon patalagya badshah permanently main kyon
Lokan de dillan te mera raj permamently hain kyon
Kande thank you par zimevari lavan main kyon
Jive mainstream ch koi meri team eni vaddi gallat fahmi
Mere baare aaj kal lokan ch hain kyon
Hon jag sara soni main Bahrain vich Michael Jackson
Ohhi log mainu karan chale broke hon main lavan
Vicodin ya lavan oxycodone
TV ch nai dikha hon main media lai nai bikkan
Saddah fans de dillan vich tikkan te nale

[Chorus – Bohemia]

Galiyan cho jaddo langnah loki karde salute mainu
Mundeyan te nale kudiyan ch dikhe mera rup mainu
Salute [x 2] luki karde salute mainu
Salute [x 2] luki karde salute mainu

[Verse 2. Bohemia]

Aj kal dastoor kuch hor mere tonvi ziyada mashhoor mere bol
Aj kal media vale kan mere tonvi ziyada mashhoor mere fan
Nale mere nal Bollywood lade jive Bollywood nu main rob karan
Fashion da style jive Hollywood ch main shop karan
Jera janda nai onu janke nai dassan
Jinnu mainu millan da shok onu milke main shock karan
Hon Jordans te G-shocks pinda ch munde karan beatbox
Oh jandene mera nah bai mere vaste aehi bot
Hon quote karan loki pan mere nah di T-shirt
Desi rap science da Einstein main aeday ch koi nai shak
Par main nal lake challan Rab nu
Jaddon galiyan chon langan main hath jorke millan sab nu
Mainu kudiyan kandiyan tere pyar ka sahara chahiye
Munde gaddi de kale shishe thalle karke vakhaan mainu double-u

[Chorus – Bohemia]

Galiyan cho jaddo langnah loki karde salute mainu
Mundeyan te nale kudiyan ch dikhe mera rup mainu
Salute [x 2] luki karde salute mainu
Salute [x 2] luki karde salute mainu
